{"tid":1615792,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"2014年1月16日 烏克蘭通過 禁蒙面法 禁頭盔法，2月22日凌晨 總統逃離基輔","createTime":"2019-10-03T07:59:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T05:42:32.000Z","uid":27718,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"58da091cf9cae207c16e59a45a20b7d35fac73c5","tid":1615792,"uid":27718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T07:59:47.000Z","msg":"2014年1月16日，國會以舉手投票方式通過法令，例如禁止民眾佩戴安全帽、口罩、面罩，禁絕五輛車同時在馬路上行駛。一連串的反示威法。<br />\n<br />\n一連串的反示威法，進一步激化政府與示威者的對立。為表不滿，示威者將家中的鍋具、單車頭盔帶到抗爭現場，諷刺禁止蒙面之類的荒誕法令。同日，示威民眾向國會進發，其間與防暴警察發生猛烈衝突。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2014年2月22日，日出之前，亞努科維奇乘坐飛機逃離基輔。國會同日決議，於5月25日舉行總統大選。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n人類總是要犯重複的錯誤。"},{"pid":"4334e65c1384ba5fa053780c901ca0766a9297a7","tid":1615792,"uid":280329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T08:01:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"091f2c103a463356da172925afc0ff6be585b8df","tid":1615792,"uid":69334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T08:06:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66ebf51e4e16fcfb7b950743cbc2c8a0d7712eb2","tid":1615792,"uid":117819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T08:09:08.000Z","msg":"林奠可以坐飛機逃走去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba4bb3ba4b1bc89dca1ffd89f1d041dde3b46f08","tid":1615792,"uid":72879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66ebf51e4e16fcfb7b950743cbc2c8a0d7712eb2","tid":1615792,"uid":117819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T08:09:08.000Z","msg":"林奠可以坐飛機逃走去邊<img src=\"/as